{"text_id":19971,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," mathematical"," connection"," between"," the"," Pythagorean"," theorem",","," commonly"," applied"," in"," electronic"," orbitals",","," and"," Kepler","'","s"," law",","," describing"," planetary"," orbits","."," Our"," work"," aims"," to"," unify"," these"," seemingly"," disparate"," concepts",","," seeking"," to"," reveal"," a"," profound"," underlying"," structure"," that"," governs"," both"," the"," behavior"," of"," electrons"," and"," celestial"," bodies","."," By"," combining"," the"," mathematical"," frameworks"," of"," both"," theories",","," we"," derive"," a"," novel"," equation"," that"," describes"," the"," relationship"," between"," the"," distance"," of"," an"," electron"," from"," the"," nucleus"," and"," its"," energy"," level","."," This"," equation"," is"," then"," applied"," to"," simulate"," the"," behavior"," of"," electrons"," in"," atomic"," systems",","," demonstrating"," a"," remarkable"," correspondence"," with"," experimental"," data","."," Furthermore",","," by"," introducing"," a"," novel"," parameter"," that"," accounts"," for"," the"," planetary"," mass",","," we"," successfully"," model"," the"," orbits"," of"," celestial"," bodies",","," accurately"," reproducing"," Kepler","'","s"," law","."," Our"," findings"," have"," significant"," implications"," for"," the"," development"," of"," quantum"," mechanics"," and"," the"," understanding"," of"," celestial"," dynamics",","," highlighting"," the"," potential"," for"," a"," deeper",","," unified"," understanding"," of"," physical"," phenomena","."," This"," research"," provides"," a"," crucial"," step"," towards"," recon","ciling"," the"," fundamental"," principles"," of"," quantum"," mechanics"," and"," classical"," astronomy","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}